@AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001

###

# -----------------------
# Documents Controller
# -----------------------

### Get All Documents
GET {{AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress}}/api/Documents
X-User-Id: david123
Accept: application/json

### Get Indexer Status
GET {{AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress}}/api/Documents/indexer-status
Accept: application/json

### Upload Document (Multipart Example)
POST {{AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress}}/api/Documents/upload
X-User-Id: david123
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

General
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a sample text file content for testing the RAG system upload.
--boundary--

### Delete Document
DELETE {{AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress}}/api/Documents/test.txt
X-User-Id: david123

### Get Document Preview URL
GET {{AzureRAGSystem.Web_HostAddress}}/api/Documents/preview/test.txt

